column5: alarm went off at 3am got out of the house at 4:15am arrived and launched at 6am fished left at 5pm. i was hoping for maybe an accidental musky, but that didn't happened..  not much to show for the day but bass

Fish don't look too bad, better than what I have been catching. I can't make any reports comp is screwed so sorry for letting you down team 3, oh and I have a new entry for us   Thanks for the pics kevin
sounds like a long but fun day for you ... those are some nice fish after the cold front!
Great job kevin!  At least you got into some nice sized fish....the muskie will be there the next time too...go get em then!
hmm i dont remember posting this, they are largies of course, xrap have u hacked my account? lol           hahahahahha 2007, shhhh its early still
Way to go Kevin.You got your self some nice looking bass there.Keep up the good work.Hope to see more of your posts. Dan
Nice bass Kevin.  Looks like you had an awsome day weather wise to fish.
